abstract: New York Liberty defeat Indiana Fever, 86-79, in WNBA action.
lead_paragraph: Tina Charles scored 21 points and Essence Carson added 14 for the Liberty (2-1), who had 23 assists on 29 baskets.

headline.main: Strong Third Quarter Lifts the Liberty
